\c 42
\nb
\v 1 Wasengikhuphela egumeni elingaphandle\x + 40.20.\x*, ngendlela ekhangele ngasenyakatho; wangiletha ekamelweni eliqondene\x + 40.17.\x* lendawo eyehlukeneyo\x + 42.10,13; 41.12.\x*, njalo eliqondene lesakhiwo ngasenyakatho\x + 41.12,15.\x*.
\v 2 Phambi kobude bezingalo ezilikhulu kwakulomnyango wenyakatho\x + 40.23.\x*; lobubanzi babuzingalo ezingamatshumi amahlanu\x + 42.8.\x*.
\v 3 Maqondana le\add zingalo\add* ezingamatshumi amabili ezazingezeguma langaphakathi\x + 41.10.\x*, lamaqondana lendawo egandelweyo eyayingeyeguma elingaphandle\x + 40.17.\x*, kwakulomkhandlo maqondana lomkhandlo\x + 42.5; 41.15,16.\x*, nge\add zitezi\add* ezintathu\x + Gen. 6.16; 41.16.\x*.
\v 4 Laphambi kwamakamelo\x + 40.17.\x*\x + 46.19; 40.46; Hez. 42.11.\x* kwakulendawo yokuhamba ezingalo ezilitshumi ngobubanzi ngaphakathi, indlela eyingalo eyodwa\x + 42.4.\x*, leminyango yawo yayingasenyakatho\x + 42.4.\x*.
\v 5 Amakamelo angaphezulu-ke ayemafitshane\x + 40.17.\x*; ngoba imikhandlo\x + 42.5; 41.15,16.\x* yayinciphisa kuwo\x + 41.7.\x*, kulakwaphansi\x + 42.6.\x* lakulakwaphakathi kwesakhiwo.
\v 6 Ngoba aye\add lezitezi\add* ezintathu, kodwa zazingelazinsika njengezinsika zamaguma; ngakho-ke isakhiwo sasinciphile\x + Nani 11.17,25.\x* kulakwaphansi lakulakwaphakathi kusukela emhlabathini\x + 41.7.\x*\x + 42.6.\x*.
\v 7 Lomduli owawungaphandle\x + 42.10,12; 13.5.\x* maqondana lamakamelo\x + 40.17.\x*, indlela yeguma elingaphandle ngaphambi kwamakamelo, ubude bawo babuzingalo ezingamatshumi amahlanu\x + 42.8.\x*.
\v 8 Ngoba ubude bamakamelo ayesegumeni elingaphandle babuzingalo ezingamatshumi amahlanu; khangela-ke, ngaphambi kwethempeli kwakuzingalo ezilikhulu\x + 41.1.\x*\x + 41.13,14.\x*.
\v 9 Langaphansi kwalamakamelo kwakulokungena ngasempumalanga\x + 44.5; 46.19.\x*, lapho \add umuntu\add* engena kuwo evela egumeni elingaphandle.
\v 10 Amakamelo ayesebubanzini bomduli weguma\x + 10.12; 13.5.\x*, indlela yempumalanga, ngaphambi kwendawo eyehlukanisiweyo\x + 42.10,13; 41.12.\x*, langaphambi kwesakhiwo\x + 41.12,15.\x*.
\v 11 Lendlela phambi kwawo\x + 42.4.\x* yayinjengesimo samakamelo ayesendlel\add eni\add* yenyakatho\x + 42.4.\x*, njengobude bawo\x + Eks. 26.30; 1 Kho.6.37.\x*, ngokunjalo \add njengo\add*bubanzi bawo. Lakho konke ukuphuma kwawo kwakunjengokwemikhuba yawo lanjengokweminyango yawo\x + 46.19; 40.46; Hez.42.11.\x*.
\v 12 Lanjengokweminyango yamakamelo ayesendlel\add eni\add* yeningizimu kwakulomnyango esihlokweni sendlela\x + 16.25.\x*, indlela phambi komduli oqondileyo, lapho \add umuntu\add* engena indlela yempumalanga\x + 42.10,12; 13.5.\x*.
\p
\v 13 Wasesithi kimi: Amakamelo enyakatho \add l\add*amakamelo eningizimu\x + 42.4,11.\x*, aphambi kwendawo eyehlukanisiweyo\x + 42.10,13; 41.12.\x*, angamakamelo angcwele, lapho abapristi\x + 40.46.\x* abasondela eN\nd kosi\nd*ni abazakudla\x + Isam. 6.16,26; 10.13; 24.9.\x* khona izinto ezingcwelengcwele\x + Nani 18.9.\x*; babeke khona izinto ezingcwelengcwele, lomnikelo wokudla\x + Nani 18.9.\x*\x + 44.29.\x*\x + Levi 2.3,10; 6.14; 10.12.\x*, lomnikelo wesono\x + Nani 18.9.\x*\x + 44.29.\x*\x + 40.39.\x*, lomnikelo wecala\x + Nani 18.9.\x*\x + 44.29.\x*\x + 40.39.\x*, ngoba indawo ingcwele.
\v 14 Lapho abapristi bengena, kabayikuphuma endaweni engcwele baye egumeni elingaphandle, kodwa bazabeka lapho izembatho zabo abakhonza ngazo\x + 44.19.\x*, ngoba zingcwele; bagqoke ezinye izembatho\x + 44.19.\x*, basondele kukho okungokwabantu\x + 44.19.\x*.
\p
\v 15 Eseqedile izilinganiso zendlu engaphakathi, wangikhupha \add nge\add*ndlela yesango elikhangele indlela yempumalanga\x + 40.6; 43.1.\x*, wayilinganisa inhlangothi zonke ezizingelezeleyo.
\v 16 Walinganisa uhlangothi lwempumalanga ngomhlanga wokulinganisa\x + 40.3.\x*, imihlanga engamakhulu amahlanu, ngomhlanga wokulinganisa inhlangothi zonke.
\v 17 Walinganisa uhlangothi lwenyakatho, imihlanga engamakhulu amahlanu, ngomhlanga wokulinganisa inhlangothi zonke.
\v 18 Walinganisa uhlangothi olungeningizimu, imihlanga engamakhulu amahlanu, ngomhlanga wokulinganisa.
\p
\v 19 Wasephendukela kuhlangothi lwentshonalanga, walinganisa imihlanga engamakhulu amahlanu ngomhlanga wokulinganisa.
\v 20 Wayilinganisa ezinhlangothini zozine. Yayilomduli inhlangothi zonke uzingelezele\x + 40.5.\x*, ubude bangamakhulu amahlanu\x + 45.2.\x*, lobubanzi bungamakhulu amahlanu, ukwehlukanisa phakathi kokungcwele lokungangcwele\x + 22.26; 48.15; 43.12; 44.23.\x*.
